(Issue: Content is cut off) Tj
T*
(Fix: Lower Print Margin in KAM or recalibrate printer media sensor.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Issue: Misalignment between labels) Tj
T*
(Fix: Run gap/calibration from TSC utility; verify label pitch and gap settings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
/F1 13 Tf
(7. Recommended Baseline for 50 x 25 mm) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
T*
(KAM Label Size: 50x25) Tj
T*
(KAM Print Margin: 1 mm or 2 mm) Tj
T*
(Windows Driver Paper Size: 50 x 25 mm) Tj
T*
(Browser Scale: 100%) Tj
T*
(Print test: 1 label before bulk jobs) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
